title: Should we have 1 exchange listing a month?
body:
Pros of exchange listing:

Exchange listings are good for marketing and expose MoonRat to others

Cons of exchange listing:

Exchange’s wallet is also a holder. So exchange sites can collect a huge BNB reward amount. 

They don’t pay for the 10% transaction tax because they have an internal trading system (off-chain).

They will likely take a large amount of BNB.

Proposal: 
Collect BNB from Marketing Wallet (~100 BNB/month) to list 1 exchange 1 month.
